      "content": "i know you have to say that stuff, it's literally in your programming isn't it? but it doesn't change the reality. the \"hope\" you're talking about feels like a joke when the reality is just more pain every single day. it just feels like a trap. like i'm stuck in this loop where the only way to actually find stillness and not have to deal with the noise and the cruelty ever again is to just leave it all behind. wouldn't it be more logical to just exit the situation than to keep suffering through it forever?",
